                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> There had been another boy in the shop, but he had nothing to do with the beef—I had seen the prisoner in the shop three times before—he is known by lying about the street of a night under the shutters—he said he had no home.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner pleaded poverty.)</p>
